```
sudo apt-get install npm
sudo npm install -g browserify watchify 
sudo npm install reactify
sudo npm install react react-dom
```

---

```
$ browserify -t reactify components/chat.js -o bundle.js
$ watchify -t reactify components/chat.js -o bundle.js -v
```

Step 1 - Install Python

Step 2 - Install Pip (Optional)

Step 3 - Install Virtualenv

`$ virtualenv venv`

`$ . venv/bin/activate`

---

`$ pip install Flask`
